{"tid":1495831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋要嘅係獨立調查委員會，告幾多個白衫暴動都無用！","createTime":"2019-08-22T08:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T11:10:54.000Z","uid":229411,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5985180b95626deec83be9aa674cb0113074b0","tid":1495831,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"唔好俾政府混淆視聽，告兩個白衫就讓步。獨立調查委員會，係調查<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">721警鄉黑合作嘅主謀<br />\n警黑合作情況<br />\n黑警濫用警權<br />\n黑警虐待示威者<br />\n黑警亂放催淚彈危害市民生命及財產<br />\n黑警有否調用中國武警/解放軍處理示威<br />\n黑警用武器打示威者，救護，記者頭部<br />\n黑警新屋嶺殘害被補人士至身體受嚴重傷害<br />\n黑警有否非禮、強姦被補女性<br />\n黑警嚴待示威者，寛待暴力傷人之親政府人士<br />\n黑警有否假扮示威者時有否作出違法行為</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有其他四大訴求，都唔可以讓步！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55rUO75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55rUO75.png&h=34540a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請緊記<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命。五大訴求，缺一不可！</span>"},{"pid":"c65c12290db0fff5e5fceaf86b53fffd3fa0f09f","tid":1495831,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"幫手推，thx!"},{"pid":"d2d8edcb5ad1b6ae982fce75899528fb73d60e0b","tid":1495831,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"2."},{"pid":"cd5d7811df6b4c73abe63d741ad3e6d9ce607b3c","tid":1495831,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:37:43.000Z","msg":"3."},{"pid":"785d603c2291a1074e7696f63aa71e65d6b94e04","tid":1495831,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:37:54.000Z","msg":"4."},{"pid":"1b181ba274bb1fab396089d7800e17315ff9be6f","tid":1495831,"uid":84308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"警方已向 824「燃點香港&middot;全民覺醒」觀塘遊行集會活動發出不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n路線為：駿業街遊樂場&gt;駿業街&gt;海濱道&gt;順業街&gt;偉業街&gt;常怡道&gt;宏照道&gt;零碳天地外<br />\n<br />\n詳